						<summary>

						<p>Stone (No. 2) on the tank bund on the border of the village.</p>						

						<p>Vijaya Bukka Mahārāya.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka • • • • • Śōbhakṛit, Pushya ba • 1.</hi></p>						

						<p>Mentions <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Kaṭhāri-Sāḷuva Teluṅgarāya Mahārāya as ruling Beḍudūru in Pennabaḍi and records some transaction, the details of which are not clear.</p>						

